Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:13.19,Aono opch,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3\be4\fad(0,500)\alpha&H02}翱翔群空 彷彿被什麼東西給吸引一般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:18.24,Aono opch,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3\be4\fad(0,500)\alpha&H02}你瞧 邂逅即是軌跡 輕輕地靠了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:25.04,Aono opch,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3\be4\fad(0,500)\alpha&H02}向著冀望於指尖的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:28.29,Aono opch,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3\be4\fad(0,500)\alpha&H02}那輕輕劃過的飛機雲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:33.63,Aono opch,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3\be4\fad(0,500)\alpha&H02}夢想的軌跡
Comment: 0,0:22:23.69,0:22:25.50,Aono edjp,,0,0,0,,ed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:19.15,Aono edjp,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}見上げた空にただぽっかりと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.23,0:22:21.82,Aono edjp,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}白い雲　浮かぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.65,0:22:26.36,Aono edjp,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}仲間の笑い声　遠くなる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:29.32,Aono edjp,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}今日の私みたいだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.53,0:22:43.00,Aono edjp,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}小さなため息も波間にそっと隠した
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:48.01,Aono edjp,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}今日はあんな上手くやれたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.09,0:22:50.72,Aono edjp,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}今は追いつけない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.47,0:22:55.22,Aono edjp,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}頼りなげな君が強くなり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:22:58.02,Aono edjp,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}空の色も変わってく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.44,0:23:11.78,Aono edjp,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}風は悔しさも淋しさも知っているから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.07,0:23:15.66,Aono edjp,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}もう一度飛んでみよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.74,0:23:19.29,Aono edjp,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}ここからが始まり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:26.55,Aono edjp,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}昨日とは違う景色がほら広がる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.55,0:23:33.55,Aono edjp,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}微かに頷いた君が微笑むから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:40.44,Aono edjp,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}握りしめてた手をいっぱいに広げ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:44.27,Aono edjp,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}一緒に飛ぼう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:19.15,Aono edch,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}抬頭仰望藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.23,0:22:21.82,Aono edch,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}只見那悠遊的白雲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.65,0:22:26.36,Aono edch,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}夥伴們的笑聲逐漸遠去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:29.32,Aono edch,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}彷彿今日的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.53,0:22:43.00,Aono edch,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}輕輕地嘆一口氣 將它藏在浪花之間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:48.01,Aono edch,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}今天明明如此順利
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.09,0:22:50.72,Aono edch,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}現在卻已遙不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.47,0:22:55.22,Aono edch,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}不可靠的妳逐漸成長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:22:58.02,Aono edch,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}天空的顏色也隨之流轉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.44,0:23:11.78,Aono edch,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}風能夠體會你的悔恨與悲寂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.07,0:23:15.66,Aono edch,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}再度展翅高飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.74,0:23:19.29,Aono edch,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}現在才正要開始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:26.55,Aono edch,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}看吧 這與昨天截然不同的開闊視野
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.55,0:23:33.55,Aono edch,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}輕輕地頷首 因為你的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:40.44,Aono edch,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}張大那緊握著的雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:44.27,Aono edch,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}一起翱翔吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,subtitle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.90,0:00:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}為什麼是美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}學姊要送講義去給明日香學姊呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.45,0:00:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沒差啦 有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真白妳也因為下雨不用練習對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.86,0:00:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}就陪我一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}哎呀 突然被告白了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:38.73,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.73,0:00:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}學姊 我的回答當然是 Yes囉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.57,0:00:49.54,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那唯一的答案 就在那片天空之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.34,0:00:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這個聲音...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.74,0:00:52.50,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}永無止盡的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:55.39,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}跨越黑暗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.85,0:00:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}她在唱歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:00:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}響徹於心底的天空霸者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}傑菲利翁
Comment: 0,0:01:06.41,0:02:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,op
Comment: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,staff
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}總覺得好虧喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那首歌是傑飛利翁的主題曲吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那是在我小時候播過的機器人動畫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}一事無成的主角呢 竟然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}怎樣啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}一坐上了傑菲利翁後就所向無敵了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是明日香傳來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}非常謝謝妳們幫我送講義來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:02:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我已經從媽媽那裡拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沒發現妳們有來真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}手機能借我一下嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}幹嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳剛才在唱傑菲利翁的主題曲吧? 下次一起傑菲一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}她回了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}什麼傑菲傑菲啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我覺得這應該是「務必務必」的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我不是那個意思 是想說 果然沒什麼好擔心的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}太好了 小明日香很有精神的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是 不好意思讓妳擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2} 昨天真是謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}新人社長 我沒去練習 真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不會啦 反正昨天也下雨 是說新人兩個字可以拿掉了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}早安 教練
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香 妳還好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是 不好意思讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}今天能來社團嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是 完全沒問題 儘管來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}果然明日香就是不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:08.14,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}也不用這麼拚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:10.31,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}儘管來 儘管來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}跟我比起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:12.35,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳才大病初癒而已 別太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不不不 不連續練個五個小時的話 我都要睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真有明日香妳的風格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明...明日香學姊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不好意思 總覺得沒辦法飛好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}先把姿勢穩定下來 試著往前飛飛看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那 接下來 High Yo Yo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那 接下來 Low Yo Yo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小明日香怎麼了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香 妳過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不好意思 完全不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真的 妳就像冒險之書消失了一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}為什麼會這樣呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}今天就做個伸展操就好 就先練到這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}教練...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}回到家之後 妳試著做做看想像練習
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}想像自己飛得很好的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}然後 明天再試著飛飛看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}辛苦各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沒關係啦 不管多有名的運動家都會有低潮期嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}即便點亮燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}即便挺身而出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}也不過是讓一事無成的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}浮上檯面而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳在做什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}咦? 傑菲利翁?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳是誰家的小孩? 迷路的小孩?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我...才不是迷路的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}欸? 那妳是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我是個愛哭又膽小 又一事無成的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳是傑菲利翁喔...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那 我們一起去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳已經要回去了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯 我們好不容易...變得這麼要好了說...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這個給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那個本來就壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳在做什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}聽說妳不會飛了 這不是飛到這裡來了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}來 便當 妳忘在教室裡囉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}非常感謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳沒戴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳的髮飾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}總覺得 有種不能戴的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}也許這雙 翅膀並不是我自己的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我從小就很嚮往在空中飛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}想要改變一事無成的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}所以 來到久奈島 第一次飛的時候 我真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:09:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}開始飛FC 拚命地練習 也遇到了很多厲害的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}然後 我變得非常快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我也覺得乾同學的FC真的很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我開始想 原來還有人能做到這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那我是不是也能變得更厲害呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但 我這只是在自我陶醉而已吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}在和乾同學的比賽中 我什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}還是一事無成 完全沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}至今為止 我身上的翅膀 只不過是從小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}和教練那裡借來的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}所以 我很害怕無能為力的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}然後就飛不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:10:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}一個人練習 總覺得好空虛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}因為小明日香說她今天也想做想像練習嘛 沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,CM
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我...為什麼會在這裡呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳在說什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明明是妳自己擺出一副茫然的表情站在我家前面的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我想說要回妳訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}結果手機沒電了 就想說該怎麼辦呢 所以就...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}所以妳就直接登門拜訪了喔? 還真有明日香學姊的風格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}話說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}為什麼真白妳也在這裡啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}因為美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}學姊妳跟我說明日香學姊在這裡 我才飛奔過來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}絕對不是想趁機來吃學姊的親手料理喔 絕對不是那樣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不好意思 讓妳們擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那就趕快開動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好 我要開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我要開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}今天我試著煎了鍋貼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}用了飛魚的魚漿 也放了很多顎骨高湯喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:12:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真是太好吃了 充滿學姊的愛的飛魚鍋貼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}才沒有愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好吃吧 喀喀喀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是 非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}今天就住我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}住...住下來...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}學姊...我要成為美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}學姊的抱真白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那個 妳可以快點吃一吃嗎? 我還要收拾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:33.77,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}唉唷 學姊 不行啦 不行 怎麼可以這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那個 對不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}給小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:12:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}社團請假單
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那是因為...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}又是為什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我? 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不管看幾次都很帥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真白 妳給我滾去其他地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}怎麼這樣? 我是沒人要的孩子嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我現在的心情就像被丟棄的小貓一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是是 丟了丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我知道了 不打擾妳們了 我走就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳們就盡情卿卿我我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這種照片到底是從哪裡翻出來的啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我也想看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}呃 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這個男孩子是誰啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}算了 反正很常被認錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}反重力鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:14:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是我的生日禮物 那時候很開心 很常自己一個人到處飛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}鞋子漸漸變髒 而我也到處找人比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2} 看起來好開心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但因為我做事都是三分鐘熱度 不知不覺中也漸漸不碰Flying Circus了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}從明日香進來之後 我又因為心血來潮開始飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但這次 我逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我以為我和真藤同學比了一場好比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}其實根本沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但是 明日香妳卻讓他認真起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我好不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}覺得無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}在和乾同學一戰中 真藤同學輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我不想相信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我開始害怕 開始迷失自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但是 明日香妳卻說他們很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}只覺得 我比不上妳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真藤同學也是 明明輸得那麼慘 卻完全沒退縮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不如說 反而讓他幹勁滿滿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}會感到害怕 是因為我很享受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我完全無法享受其樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}所以 我決定要放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}到底怎麼了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真難看呢 我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}才沒那回事 小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}很帥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}因為 小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}把我帶進了天空的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}看著小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}的身姿 我希望自己有朝一日也能飛得那麼美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}謝...謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香妳沒問題的 妳確實是用自己的翅膀在飛行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}雖然這話沒有根據啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沒有嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這麼晚了喔? 差不多該睡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:21.08,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那 幫我把被子鋪一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}棄貓真白 應該不會來把我撿回去吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:23.08,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真是的 不過 也沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}無敵的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}繞著群星流轉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}答案一定就在那片天空之中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}永無止盡的世界 跨越黑暗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:17:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}響徹於心底的天空霸者 傑菲利翁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳們兩個該不會都把我給忘了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 是這樣啊 妳們進入兩人世界裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那還真是抱歉啊 我真是個電燈泡 妳們有在聽嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}對不起啦 小真白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}算了 是無所謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}快一點 要遲到了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}幹嘛啦? 快衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}幹嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}請和我比賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}答案 就在那片天空之中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}原來那只是普通的假單喔?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是的 因為我想休息一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}然後 美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}妳呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我接下來要和明日香比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}然後 如果我輸給明日香的話 我就回社團
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}說什麼答案就在那片天空之中 明日香妳還太嫩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}天上只談勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我絕對會贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}其實我有點害怕和明日香一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我贏了的話 小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}就會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}各就各位 比賽開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}有好好地在飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}看來是回想起來了呢 飛行的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香學姊 得分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}休想通過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}讓我們來大幹一場吧 小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香 那是我的台詞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}學姊 得分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}一比...二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}天真
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}學姊 得分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}一比三
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}果然很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但 我也不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香學姊 得分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我要上囉 明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好高
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那是...三角飛行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}{\fs30\pos(1065,975)}Delta Force
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是明日香自創的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我啊 終於懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}會害怕 是因為我找到了第一次能讓我認真 能讓我著迷的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但是我 也許還是有點害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我啊 總之就先向上飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我覺得答案果然就在那片天空之中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}學姊 雖然妳贏了 但 這個該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊...妳有筆嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.17,0:21:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我不是回來 而是再次加入
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這樣妳就是新社員了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}從今天開始請叫我真白學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}為什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:34.89,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}無敵的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:38.44,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}繞著群星流轉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這就是傑肥利翁喔?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:43.94,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}答案一定就在那片天空之中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}學姊妳說錯了 這樣可傑菲不了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香的那個翅膀 原來是傑肥利翁的翅膀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:49.95,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}永無止盡的世界 跨越黑暗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}就說妳說錯了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這是我小時候 這座島上某個孩子給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:53.95,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}響徹於心底的天空霸者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}島上某個孩子?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:58.42,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}傑菲利翁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.99,0:21:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}到底是誰呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}有點女版教練的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.96,0:21:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好噁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}因為是小時候的事了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 是說我以前找陌生人比賽時 好像也遇過這樣的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}會不會是同一個人啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不知道欸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}算了 隨便啦
