Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.69,0:23:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我們的FC真美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 六個小時喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.65,0:23:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}教練
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.11,0:23:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那也是為了FC嗎?
